            <!-- ── SECTION 01: ETCD ── -->
            <section class="doc-section" id="etcd">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num">01</span>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="section-title">Setup Etcd <span class="dim">/ Discovery Layer</span></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="section-body">
                    Etcd bertindak sebagai <strong>distributed consensus store</strong> untuk seluruh cluster.
                    Semua node Patroni akan melaporkan status, leader election, dan konfigurasi DCS ke
                    endpoint <code>192.168.1.15:2379</code>. Pastikan service ini running sebelum menjalankan Patroni.
                </p>

                <div class="info-box note">
                    <span class="icon">NOTE</span>
                    <p class="text"><strong>listen-client-urls</strong> wajib di-bind ke <code>0.0.0.0</code> supaya semua node bisa reach. Tapi <strong>advertise-client-urls</strong> harus pakai IP spesifik, bukan wildcard.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="code-block">
                    <div class="code-header">
                        <div class="code-header-left">
                            <div class="code-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
                            <span class="code-filename">etcd.service — ExecStart flags</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="code-lang">shell</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="code-body">
                        <div class="line-nums">
                            <span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span>
                            <span>5</span><span>6</span><span>7</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-content"><span class="cm"># Bind ke semua interface agar bisa di-reach dari node lain</span>
<span class="kw">--listen-client-urls</span> <span class="st">http://0.0.0.0:2379</span>

<span class="cm"># Advertise IP statis node etcd ke cluster</span>
<span class="kw">--advertise-client-urls</span> <span class="st">http://192.168.1.15:2379</span>

<span class="cm"># Verifikasi endpoint berjalan</span>
<span class="nm">etcdctl</span> <span class="op">--endpoints</span>=http://192.168.1.15:2379 endpoint health</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box warn">
                    <span class="icon">WARN</span>
                    <p class="text">Jika <strong>firewalld</strong> aktif, buka port <code>2379</code> dan <code>2380</code> sebelum melanjutkan. Cluster tidak akan terbentuk jika port tersebut diblokir.</p>
                </div>
            </section>


            <!-- ── SECTION 02: PATRONI ── -->
            <section class="doc-section" id="patroni">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num">02</span>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="section-title">Konfigurasi Patroni <span class="dim">/ Node Manager</span></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="section-body">
                    Patroni dijalankan di atas setiap node Rocky Linux untuk memonitor proses Postgres secara lokal.
                    Terdapat dua node — <strong>pg-node-1</strong> sebagai leader (<code>192.168.1.13</code>) dan
                    <strong>pg-node-2</strong> sebagai replica (<code>192.168.1.14</code>). Keduanya mengarah ke
                    Etcd di <code>192.168.1.15:2379</code>.
                </p>

                <p class="section-body" style="margin-top:-12px;">
                    Field yang <strong>berbeda antar node</strong>: <code>name</code>, <code>restapi.connect_address</code>,
                    dan <code>postgresql.connect_address</code>. Sisanya identik.
                </p>

                <!-- pg-node-1 -->
                <div class="code-block">
                    <div class="code-header">
                        <div class="code-header-left">
                            <div class="code-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
                            <span class="code-filename">/etc/patroni.yml — pg-node-1 (leader · 192.168.1.13)</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="code-lang">yaml</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="code-body">
                        <div class="line-nums">
                            <span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span><span>5</span>
                            <span>6</span><span>7</span><span>8</span><span>9</span><span>10</span>
                            <span>11</span><span>12</span><span>13</span><span>14</span><span>15</span>
                            <span>16</span><span>17</span><span>18</span><span>19</span><span>20</span>
                            <span>21</span><span>22</span><span>23</span><span>24</span><span>25</span>
                            <span>26</span><span>27</span><span>28</span><span>29</span><span>30</span>
                            <span>31</span><span>32</span><span>33</span><span>34</span><span>35</span>
                            <span>36</span><span>37</span><span>38</span><span>39</span><span>40</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-content"><span class="kw">scope</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">postgres-ha</span>
<span class="kw">name</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">pg-node-1</span>
<span class="kw">etcd3</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">hosts</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">192.168.1.15:2379</span>

<span class="kw">restapi</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">listen</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">0.0.0.0:8008</span>
  <span class="kw">connect_address</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">192.168.1.13:8008</span>

<span class="kw">postgresql</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">listen</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">0.0.0.0:5432</span>
  <span class="kw">connect_address</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">192.168.1.13:5432</span>
  <span class="kw">data_dir</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">/var/lib/pgsql/14/data</span>
  <span class="kw">bin_dir</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">/usr/pgsql-14/bin</span>
  <span class="kw">pgpass</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">/tmp/pgpass0</span>
  <span class="kw">pg_hba</span><span class="pu">:</span>
    <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">host replication replicator 192.168.1.0/24 md5</span>
    <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">host all all 0.0.0.0/0 md5</span>
  <span class="kw">authentication</span><span class="pu">:</span>
    <span class="kw">replication</span><span class="pu">:</span>
      <span class="kw">username</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">replicator</span>
      <span class="kw">password</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">repl_password</span>
    <span class="kw">superuser</span><span class="pu">:</span>
      <span class="kw">username</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">postgres</span>
      <span class="kw">password</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">super_password</span>

<span class="kw">bootstrap</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">dcs</span><span class="pu">:</span>
    <span class="kw">ttl</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">30</span>
    <span class="kw">loop_wait</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">10</span>
    <span class="kw">retry_timeout</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">10</span>
    <span class="kw">maximum_lag_on_failover</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">1048576</span>
    <span class="kw">postgresql</span><span class="pu">:</span>
      <span class="kw">use_pg_rewind</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">true</span>
      <span class="kw">parameters</span><span class="pu">:</span>
        <span class="kw">wal_level</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">logical</span>
  <span class="kw">initdb</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">auth-host: md5</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">auth-local: trust</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">encoding: UTF8</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">locale: en_US.UTF-8</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">data-checksums</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="height:20px;"></div>

                <!-- pg-node-2 -->
                <div class="code-block">
                    <div class="code-header">
                        <div class="code-header-left">
                            <div class="code-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
                            <span class="code-filename">/etc/patroni.yml — pg-node-2 (replica · 192.168.1.14)</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="code-lang">yaml</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="code-body">
                        <div class="line-nums">
                            <span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span><span>5</span>
                            <span>6</span><span>7</span><span>8</span><span>9</span><span>10</span>
                            <span>11</span><span>12</span><span>13</span><span>14</span><span>15</span>
                            <span>16</span><span>17</span><span>18</span><span>19</span><span>20</span>
                            <span>21</span><span>22</span><span>23</span><span>24</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-content"><span class="kw">scope</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">postgres-ha</span>
<span class="kw">name</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">pg-node-2</span>
<span class="kw">etcd3</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">hosts</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">192.168.1.15:2379</span>

<span class="kw">restapi</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">listen</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">0.0.0.0:8008</span>
  <span class="kw">connect_address</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">192.168.1.14:8008</span>

<span class="kw">postgresql</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">listen</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">0.0.0.0:5432</span>
  <span class="kw">connect_address</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">192.168.1.14:5432</span>
  <span class="kw">data_dir</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">/var/lib/pgsql/14/data</span>
  <span class="kw">bin_dir</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">/usr/pgsql-14/bin</span>
  <span class="kw">pgpass</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">/tmp/pgpass0</span>
  <span class="kw">pg_hba</span><span class="pu">:</span>
    <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">host replication replicator 127.0.0.1/32 md5</span>
    <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">host replication replicator 192.168.1.0/24 md5</span>
    <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">host all all 0.0.0.0/0 md5</span>
    <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">local all all trust</span>
  <span class="kw">authentication</span><span class="pu">:</span>
    <span class="kw">replication</span><span class="pu">:</span>
      <span class="kw">username</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">replicator</span>
      <span class="kw">password</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">repl_password</span>
    <span class="kw">superuser</span><span class="pu">:</span>
      <span class="kw">username</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">postgres</span>
      <span class="kw">password</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">super_password</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box note" style="margin-top:20px;">
                    <span class="icon">NOTE</span>
                    <p class="text">pg-node-2 menambahkan <code>127.0.0.1/32</code> dan <code>local all all trust</code> di <strong>pg_hba</strong>. Password <code>repl_password</code> dan <code>super_password</code> harus <strong>identik</strong> di kedua node.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box tip" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <span class="icon">TIP</span>
                    <p class="text">Gunakan <code>patronictl -c /etc/patroni.yml list</code> untuk melihat status semua member cluster secara real-time.</p>
                </div>
            </section>


            <!-- ── SECTION 03: FAILOVER ── -->
            <section class="doc-section" id="failover">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num">03</span>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="section-title">Failover Logic <span class="dim">/ Auto-Election</span></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="section-body">
                    Ketika primary node tidak responsif selama <strong>ttl (default 30s)</strong>, Patroni akan
                    memulai proses <strong>leader election</strong> via Etcd. Replica dengan WAL position
                    paling terkini akan dipromosikan menjadi primary baru.
                </p>

                <div class="code-block">
                    <div class="code-header">
                        <div class="code-header-left">
                            <div class="code-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
                            <span class="code-filename">patroni.yml — bootstrap.dcs (dari pg-node-1)</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="code-lang">yaml</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="code-body">
                        <div class="line-nums">
                            <span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span><span>5</span>
                            <span>6</span><span>7</span><span>8</span><span>9</span><span>10</span>
                            <span>11</span><span>12</span><span>13</span><span>14</span><span>15</span>
                            <span>16</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-content"><span class="kw">bootstrap</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="kw">dcs</span><span class="pu">:</span>
    <span class="kw">ttl</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">30</span>           <span class="cm"># detik sebelum leader dianggap mati</span>
    <span class="kw">loop_wait</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">10</span>      <span class="cm"># interval health check</span>
    <span class="kw">retry_timeout</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">10</span>
    <span class="kw">maximum_lag_on_failover</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="nm">1048576</span>  <span class="cm"># 1MB max WAL lag</span>
    <span class="kw">postgresql</span><span class="pu">:</span>
      <span class="kw">use_pg_rewind</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">true</span>
      <span class="kw">parameters</span><span class="pu">:</span>
        <span class="kw">wal_level</span><span class="pu">:</span> <span class="st">logical</span>
  <span class="kw">initdb</span><span class="pu">:</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">auth-host: md5</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">auth-local: trust</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">encoding: UTF8</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">locale: en_US.UTF-8</span>
  <span class="pu">-</span> <span class="st">data-checksums</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box note" style="margin-top:20px;">
                    <span class="icon">NOTE</span>
                    <p class="text"><code>bootstrap.dcs</code> hanya dibaca saat <strong>cluster pertama kali dibuat</strong>. Setelah itu konfigurasi DCS disimpan di Etcd dan perubahan harus dilakukan via <code>patronictl edit-config</code>.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box warn" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <span class="icon">WARN</span>
                    <p class="text"><code>maximum_lag_on_failover: 1048576</code> berarti replica dengan WAL lag lebih dari <strong>1MB</strong> tidak akan dipromosikan. Sesuaikan nilainya dengan toleransi data loss kamu.</p>
                </div>
            </section>


            <!-- ── TOPOLOGY ── -->
            <section class="doc-section" id="topology">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num">─</span>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="section-title">Cluster Topology <span class="dim">/ Network Map</span></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="topology">
                    <div class="topo-grid">
                        <div class="topo-node primary">
                            <div class="topo-name">pg-node-1</div>
                            <div class="topo-ip">192.168.1.13</div>
                            <span class="topo-role primary-role">leader</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="topo-arrow">→</div>
                        <div class="topo-node etcd">
                            <div class="topo-name">etcd-01</div>
                            <div class="topo-ip">192.168.1.15</div>
                            <span class="topo-role etcd-role">consensus</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="topo-arrow">←</div>
                        <div class="topo-node">
                            <div class="topo-name">pg-node-2</div>
                            <div class="topo-ip">192.168.1.14</div>
                            <span class="topo-role replica-role">replica</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>


            <!-- ── DEBUG TRACE ── -->
            <section class="doc-section" id="debug">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num">─</span>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="section-title">Debug Trace <span class="dim">/ Etcd Payload</span></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="section-body">
                    Raw JSON payload yang diterima dari Etcd cluster. Data ini di-render via Go template
                    dan digunakan untuk men-populate status di atas.
                </p>

                <div class="terminal-block">
                    <div class="terminal-header">
                        <div class="code-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
                        <span class="terminal-title">etcd-payload — last response</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="terminal-body">
<span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">curl http://192.168.1.15:2379/v3/kv/range | jq .</span>
<br>
<span class="out">{</span>
  <span class="key">"leader"</span><span class="out">:</span>  <span class="val">"<span class="tmpl">{{ .leader_name }}</span>"</span><span class="out">,</span>
  <span class="key">"primary"</span><span class="out">:</span> <span class="val">"<span class="tmpl">{{ .primary }}</span>"</span><span class="out">,</span>
  <span class="key">"members"</span><span class="out">:</span> <span class="val">[...]</span>
<span class="out">}</span>
<br>
<span class="out">── raw template output ──────────────</span>
<span class="tmpl">{{ .raw_json }}</span>
<br>
<span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cursor"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </main>
    </div>


